      <container name="إذ يشير" eId="container_2">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="bold italic">إذ يشير</span> إلى قراراته السابقة المتعلقة بالسودان، ولا سيما القرارات <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1591 (2005)">1591</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1591 (2005)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1591 (2005)">2005</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1591 (2005)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1651 (2005)">1651</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1651 (2005)"> </a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1651 (2005)">(</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1651 (2005)">2005</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1651 (2005)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1665 (2006)">1665</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1665 (2006)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1665 (2006)">2006</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1665 (2006)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1672 (2006)">1672</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1672 (2006)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1672 (2006)">2006</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1672 (2006)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1713 (2006)">1713</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1713 (2006)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1713 (2006)">2006</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1713 (2006)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1779 (2007)">1779</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1779 (2007)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1779 (2007)">2007</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1779 (2007)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1841 (2008)">1841</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1841 (2008)"> </a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1841 (2008)">(</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1841 (2008)">2008</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1841 (2008)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1891 (2009)">1891</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1891 (2009)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1891 (2009)">2009</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1891 (2009)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1945 (2010)">1945</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1945 (2010)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1945 (2010)">2010</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1945 (2010)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1982 (2011)">1982</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1982 (2011)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1982 (2011)">2011</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/1982 (2011)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2035 (2012)">2035</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2035 (2012)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2035 (2012)">2012</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2035 (2012)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2091 (2013)">2091</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2091 (2013)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2091 (2013)">2013</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2091 (2013)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2138 (2014)">2138</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2138 (2014)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2138 (2014)">2014</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2138 (2014)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2200 (2015)">2200</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2200 (2015)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2200 (2015)">2015</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2200 (2015)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2265 (2016)">2265</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2265 (2016)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2265 (2016)">2016</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2265 (2016)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2340 (2017)">2340</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2340 (2017)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2340 (2017)">2017</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2340 (2017)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2400 (2018)">2400</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2400 (2018)"> (</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2400 (2018)">2018</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2400 (2018)">)</a> و <a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2455 (2019)">2455</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2455 (2019)"> </a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2455 (2019)">(</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2455 (2019)">2019</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/RES/2455 (2019)">)</a>، وإلى بيانه الرئاسي المؤرخ 11 كانون الأول/ديسمبر 2018 (<a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/PRST/2018/19">S/PRST/</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/PRST/2018/19">2018</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/PRST/2018/19">/</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/PRST/2018/19">19</a>)،</p>
      </container>
      <container name="وإذ يقرر" eId="container_3">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="bold italic">وإذ يقرر</span> أن الحالة في السودان لا تزال تشكل تهديدا للسلام والأمن الدوليين في المنطقة،</p>
      </container>
      <container name="وإذ يشير" eId="container_4">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="bold italic">وإذ يشير</span> إلى التقرير النهائي لفريق الخبراء المعني بالسودان (<a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/2020/36">S/</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/2020/36">2020</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/2020/36">/</a><a href="https://undocs.org/ar/S/2020/36">36</a>)،</p>
      </container>
      <container name="وإذ يتصرف" eId="container_5">
        <p xml:space="preserve">	<span class="bold italic">وإذ يتصرف</span> بموجب الفصل السابع من ميثاق الأمم المتحدة،</p>
      </container>
